                <div class="activity-price">From $40/person</div>
            </div>
            <div class="activity-detail">
                <i class="fas fa-ship"></i>
                <h3>Island Tours</h3>
                <p>Discover the beauty of nearby islands with our guided boat tours, including lunch and refreshments.</p>
                <div class="activity-price">From $100/person</div>
            </div>
            <div class="activity-detail">
                <i class="fas fa-tree"></i>
                <h3>Wilpattu Safari</h3>
                <p>Experience wildlife in Wilpattu National Park, home to leopards, elephants, and diverse bird species.</p>
                <div class="activity-price">From $120/person</div>
            </div>
            <div class="activity-detail">
                <i class="fas fa-sun"></i>
                <h3>Beach Activities</h3>
                <p>Relax on pristine beaches with volleyball, beach walks, and sunset viewing experiences.</p>
